      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Calling all restoration fans and DIY enthusiasts! This vehicle is ready for a dedicated new owner to bring it back to its former glory. While it is currently in poor condition and will require a significant mechanical and cosmetic overhaul, it serves as the perfect canvas for a rewarding project. If you're looking for a car with potential and are ready to put in the work, this is the one for you!",
